// ============================================================
// go.zy — entry point, English — for terminals where typing CJK is inconvenient
//
// The four entry points differ only in the locale they preselect.
// Every one of them can switch language from the setup screen —
// this just decides which language the setup screen itself is in.
//
//   zymbol run go.zy
// ============================================================

<# ./対局 => 対局

対局::開始("en")
